earchers to understand and identified the limitations lay in these methods. In this survey, ED models for text data from various Social Network sites (SNs) are analyzed based on domain type, detection methods, type of detection task. In addition, main categories for unsupervised detection methods are explicitly mentioned with revising their related works. Moreover, the major open challenges faced by researchers for building ED models are explained and discussed in detail. The main objective of this survey paper is to provide a complete view of the recent developments in ED field. Hence, help scholars to identify the limitations of existing ED models for text data and help them to recognize the interesting future works directions. ¬© 2020 Wafa Zubair AL-Dyani, Farzana Kabir Ahmad and Siti Sakira Kamaruddin.'),(79,_binary 'data:image/jpeg;base64,','Yusof, Yuhanis','UUM',_binary 'Äcnumpy.core.multiarray\n_reconstruct\nq\0cnumpy\nndarray\nqK\0Öqc_codecs\nencode\nqX\0\0\0bqX\0\0\0latin1qÜqRqáqRq	(KM\0Öq\ncnumpy\ndtype\nqX\0\0\0f4qâàáq\rRq(KX\0\0\0<qNNNJˇˇˇˇJˇˇˇˇK\0tqbâhX\Ê\0\0!?¬§¬ö¬≥>E;A¬æ\'√Æ¬ß¬ø¬à√º+? $¬ø√Çe#>4e¬ø√à√ª^?¬ê√∑\'?√ï√∂x?)|l>xq>=√µ ¬ø√è√Ç√°¬æ¬º√ò√Ñ>	√∂√≤¬æ¬Ä√âl¬ª√â¬∏	?¬êy¬ë>√ò>√ëHt?¬à√ú√ñ=w√Ω¬™¬æ√ê¬Ü√®>\0√õ_?)N¬ø¬π¬à¬≠¬æ¬å√¶√ö¬Ω¬Ω√∞d?¬®√àv¬ø¬ï3¬ø√ã¬ó¬æ¬†v√ì¬ø5Q√∑¬æY√Çt?√¨\0|>X¬±r¬ø<@√Äk¬Ø¬ü>¬Ö¬™h>¬ΩP¬§¬æ¬≠@U√âP¬Ω¬π¬Ω√è¬æ¬ºY√Ö¬æ√ó√Ü√Ø>√ì%¬ó>√≠√®>√É¬á√ª<¬∂¬ø¬π;&¬æL¬∏\'¬æ7G¬ü?√¨,¬≤?√íD¬æ]¬ö=√ù2¬ø¬©√°¬Ü?¬ï2¬à¬ΩM¬°√é¬º%√ß¬æD¬∫>+j¬≠¬æ¬ù√Ü¬à>¬ëO√ô¬æM√´b?8;¬ò?√π√á√í>¬Å4¬≠?!n¬ç¬Ω√å√çl?¬ªD\0?]√Ä¬î>¬¥~¬¥>√ÑE?8¬™¬ô>√≥√Ä√Ω¬Ω¬ö1¬ø4\\;?s¬µ√Å¬æ#o¬å¬æ¬µ√â¬ö>√Ä,O¬º$¬ì¬Ωq!¬É>¬ë¬ê¬ø√ÉD√Ä¬æ¬°√•R¬øs√Å¬Ø>¬ãd?¬ç8	?[%¬¥>√çt¬Ω¬ò√ü√ç?¬ñl?¬®qu>Pm¬ê¬ø√∞\r?√≠¬Ä?¬∞J¬®=√â_k?¬õ¬ç?√Ω√¶√ï>¬°L¬©?mq¬Ö¬Ω¬øX?√Å¬¨¬æ√úa¬°¬ø¬â√´\Z?1f¬Ç¬æXK√ô¬ø¬∞#¬ø¬®¬¨√ÄDv\">√ë¬∫¬æzq¬ø√†,¬ä¬øD√úK¬ø?o:?√Ä√öH?√ã√¶>¬ê	¬øtX¬æZ¬ö?¬Ö¬¶p?¬ã(5?%¬¨√î¬æs√≥¬æ√ª&{¬æ¬™¬°=E2√∑>√º¬ì<¬æu~h¬ø√ª4v>i¬¢G¬ø¬á√¢¬Ä¬Ω	v<¬ì¬Ç√¶¬øF¬°¬ø√Ü*?(V¬°?¬É¬ÑQ?¬ª√£√Ç>@¬≥¬∫¬Ω¬¥¬±h?√ã\